      "text": "pipeline/baseline.py:\n\n1. NLP Pipeline (SpaCy extraction)\n2. CoordinatorAgent (multi-agent)\n3. Self-Improvement Loop:\n   - MCP Validation\n   - ErrorLearner (fix attempts)\n   - Backtest via QC MCP\n\nReturns: StrategyResult\n  code_files, sharpe, max_dd",
