      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "AUTONOMOUS LIBRARY GENERATION (N iterations):\n\n  FOR i = 1 to count (default: 10):\n  |\n  |   +---> [1] BaselinePipeline.run(query)\n  |   |         - NLP extraction\n  |   |         - CoordinatorAgent -> multi-agent\n  |   |         - Self-improvement loop\n  |   |         - MCP backtest\n  |   |              |\n  |   |              v\n  |   |     [2] QuantPerspectiveRefiner.analyze(result)\n  |   |         - Analyze backtest metrics (Sharpe, DD, win_rate)\n  |   |         - Identify strengths/weaknesses\n  |   |              |\n  |   |              v\n  |   +---- [3] suggest_next_prompt()\n  |              - Vary indicators, asset classes, timeframes\n  |              - Expand research field based on results\n  |\n  SAVE: LibraryEntry (code_files, metadata.json, README.md)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "AUTONOMOUS LIBRARY GENERATION (N iterations):\n\n  FOR i = 1 to count (default: 10):\n  |\n  |   +---> [1] BaselinePipeline.run(query)\n  |   |         - NLP extraction\n  |   |         - CoordinatorAgent -> multi-agent\n  |   |         - Self-improvement loop\n  |   |         - MCP backtest\n  |   |              |\n  |   |              v\n  |   |     [2] QuantPerspectiveRefiner.analyze(result)\n  |   |         - Analyze backtest metrics (Sharpe, DD, win_rate)\n  |   |         - Identify strengths/weaknesses\n  |   |              |\n  |   |              v\n  |   +---- [3] suggest_next_prompt()\n  |              - Vary indicators, asset classes, timeframes\n  |              - Expand research field based on results\n  |\n  SAVE: LibraryEntry (code_files, metadata.json, README.md)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
