      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "ALPHAEVOLVE-INSPIRED GENETIC OPTIMIZATION:\n\nInput: Single algorithm OR entire library (--library)\n\n  Baseline Code --> [VariationGenerator]\n                         |\n        +----------------+----------------+\n        |                                 |\n   MUTATION (1 parent)           CROSSOVER (2 parents)\n   - indicator_change            - combine best features\n   - risk_management             - merge indicators\n   - entry_exit_logic            - blend risk approaches\n   - universe_selection\n   - timeframe_change\n        |                                 |\n        +----------------+----------------+\n                         |\n                    [QCEvaluator] --> QuantConnect Backtest\n                         |\n                    [ElitePool] --> Keep best N variants\n                         |\n                    Next Generation (until convergence)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ALPHAEVOLVE-INSPIRED GENETIC OPTIMIZATION:\n\nInput: Single algorithm OR entire library (--library)\n\n  Baseline Code --> [VariationGenerator]\n                         |\n        +----------------+----------------+\n        |                                 |\n   MUTATION (1 parent)           CROSSOVER (2 parents)\n   - indicator_change            - combine best features\n   - risk_management             - merge indicators\n   - entry_exit_logic            - blend risk approaches\n   - universe_selection\n   - timeframe_change\n        |                                 |\n        +----------------+----------------+\n                         |\n                    [QCEvaluator] --> QuantConnect Backtest\n                         |\n                    [ElitePool] --> Keep best N variants\n                         |\n                    Next Generation (until convergence)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
