      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "pipeline/quant_refiner.py:\n\nAnalyzes backtest results:\n- sharpe_ratio, max_drawdown, win_rate\n- total_return, volatility\n\nSuggests variations:\n- INDICATORS (momentum, volatility, mean_rev)\n- ASSET_CLASSES (equities, crypto, forex)\n- TIMEFRAMES (intraday, daily, weekly)\n- RISK_APPROACHES (vol_targeting, fixed_pct)\n- FACTORS (value, momentum, quality)\n\nReturns: QuantAnalysis (strengths, weaknesses, suggestions)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "pipeline/quant_refiner.py:\n\nAnalyzes backtest results:\n- sharpe_ratio, max_drawdown, win_rate\n- total_return, volatility\n\nSuggests variations:\n- INDICATORS (momentum, volatility, mean_rev)\n- ASSET_CLASSES (equities, crypto, forex)\n- TIMEFRAMES (intraday, daily, weekly)\n- RISK_APPROACHES (vol_targeting, fixed_pct)\n- FACTORS (value, momentum, quality)\n\nReturns: QuantAnalysis (strengths, weaknesses, suggestions)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
