      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "autonomous/learner.py:\n\nErrorLearner:\n- Classify errors (import, name, syntax)\n- Store error->fix mappings\n- Self-healing with learned fixes\n\nPromptRefiner (prompt_refiner.py):\n- Inject learnings into agent prompts\n- Include error avoidance patterns\n- Add success patterns\n\nLearningDatabase (SQLite):\n- GeneratedStrategy records\n- CompilationError history\n- SuccessfulFix cache",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "autonomous/learner.py:\n\nErrorLearner:\n- Classify errors (import, name, syntax)\n- Store error->fix mappings\n- Self-healing with learned fixes\n\nPromptRefiner (prompt_refiner.py):\n- Inject learnings into agent prompts\n- Include error avoidance patterns\n- Add success patterns\n\nLearningDatabase (SQLite):\n- GeneratedStrategy records\n- CompilationError history\n- SuccessfulFix cache",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
