      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "QuantConnect MCP (validation + backtest):\n- mcp/validation.py: Syntax + API validation\n- mcp/backtest.py: Run backtests via QC API\n- Returns: BacktestResult (sharpe, drawdown, returns)\n\nCrossRef API (article search):\n- tools/search_tools.py: SearchArticlesTool\n- Keyword-based academic paper search\n\nNLP Pipeline (SpaCy):\n- core/processor.py: PDFLoader, TextPreprocessor\n- HeadingDetector, SectionSplitter, KeywordAnalyzer",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "QuantConnect MCP (validation + backtest):\n- mcp/validation.py: Syntax + API validation\n- mcp/backtest.py: Run backtests via QC API\n- Returns: BacktestResult (sharpe, drawdown, returns)\n\nCrossRef API (article search):\n- tools/search_tools.py: SearchArticlesTool\n- Keyword-based academic paper search\n\nNLP Pipeline (SpaCy):\n- core/processor.py: PDFLoader, TextPreprocessor\n- HeadingDetector, SectionSplitter, KeywordAnalyzer",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
