      "text": "MODE SUMMARY:\n\n1. GENERATE (baseline): CLI -> BaselinePipeline (NLP -> CoordinatorAgent -> Self-Improvement -> MCP Backtest) -> Single Strategy\n2. AUTO (library):      CLI -> AutoMode (BaselinePipeline x N + QuantPerspectiveRefiner) -> Strategy Library\n3. EVOLVE (genetic):    CLI -> EvolutionEngine (library or single + VariationGenerator + ElitePool) -> Optimized Variants",
